dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Dane County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2023 and includes the layers 'Dane_Hydro_LINE_2023' and 'Dane_Hydro_POLY_2023.' [This is a countywide hydrolographic dataset that provides a comprehensive 2,400 scale representation of the hydrologic features in Dane County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/
